➜糖尿病上身怎麼办？妥善运用胰岛素，稳定血糖、保护胰脏！
https://pansci.asia/archives/198199	3600
<ul><li>作者／曾耀贤</li><li>本文转载自 Care Online 照护线上《<a href="https://www.careonline.com.tw/2020/11/diabetes-insulin.html">善用胰岛素，稳定血糖、保护胰脏，医师图文解说</a>》，欢迎喜欢这篇文章的朋友订阅支持&nbsp;<a href="https://www.careonline.com.tw/">Care Online</a>&nbsp;喔</li></ul>
<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img loading="lazy" width="560" height="293" src="http://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/d492a0b083916f7e94c4a2ee0d453f61-560x293.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-198208" srcset="https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/d492a0b083916f7e94c4a2ee0d453f61-560x293.jpg 560w, https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/d492a0b083916f7e94c4a2ee0d453f61-510x267.jpg 510w, https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/d492a0b083916f7e94c4a2ee0d453f61-273x143.jpg 273w, https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/d492a0b083916f7e94c4a2ee0d453f61-350x183.jpg 350w, https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/d492a0b083916f7e94c4a2ee0d453f61.jpg 740w" sizes="(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px" /></figure></div>
<p>「同学们，我被诊断出糖尿病了，大家也要注意身体啊！」阿德在大学同学的群组上留言写道：「可能是太常熬夜又不运动，毕业十年就胖了 20 几公斤。」</p>
<p>一看到讯息，同学们纷纷留言：</p>
<p>「我们还不到 35 岁，原来也会得糖尿病啊！」</p><div class="pansc-content"></script>
